overview: Cinderella Tournament 2021 Semifinal Match  Unagi Sayaka vs. Himeka  Cinderella Tournament 2021 Semifinal Match  Saya Kamitani vs. Maika  Three Way Tag Team Match (Teams determined by lottery)  Azumi-gun (Natsupoi & AZM) vs. Mina Shirakawa & Momo Watanabe vs. Giulia & Tam Nakano  Elimination Tag Team Match (The last person eliminated must join the other team)  Oedo Tai (Ruaka, Fukigen Death, Konami, Saki Kashima & Natsuko Tora) vs. STARS (Rin Kadokura, Koguma, Hanan, Starlight Kid & Mayu Iwatani)  Cinderella Tournament 2021 Final Match  Winner of Semifinal Match 1 vs. Winner of Semifinal Match 2  World of Stardom Championship  Utami Hayashishita (c) vs. Syuri
title: STARDOM Tokyo Dream Cinderella 2021
